scenes.description: An advertisement for 'holoplus+', the official hololive production app.
Pre-concert announcement showing the main key visual for 'Breaking Dimensions'.
Performance precautions and 'Attention For Visitors' slide.
Showcase of official concert merchandise, including apparel and accessories.
A long montage displaying fan-submitted messages and artwork supporting the concert.
